Entities.name: Seat
Entities.script: (function () {     var clicked = false;     this.clickDownOnEntity = function (entityID, mouseEvent) {         if (clicked){             Entities.editEntity(entityID, { color: { red: 255, green: 0, blue: 0} });             MyAvatar.endSit(Entities.localToWorldPosition(this.position, entityID), Quat.cancelOutRoll(Quat.getFront(this.orientation)));             clicked = false;         } else {             Entities.editEntity(entityID, { color: { red: 0, green: 255, blue: 0} });             MyAvatar.beginSit(Entities.localToWorldPosition(this.position, entityID), Quat.cancelOutRoll(Quat.getFront(this.orientation)));             clicked = true;         }     }; })
